{"type": "article", "id": 29230, "title": "模块化接线板", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-06T22:51:54Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 95, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160706223637WdLmq74IKVNGbXi6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>你眼中好用的接线板会有哪几个要素？最好配有多个插座，造型也要好看到至少不需要把它藏在角落里。我们之前就介绍过一款小巧的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28931.html\">接线板</a>，不过它的插头可能对一些人来说并不够用。初创公司 <a href=\"http://stackedmodular.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stacked</a> 选择一个聪明的办法，同名的接线板被设计为模块化的结构，人们可以根据需要自由地加减模块。由于每一节内部都采用了转轴的设计，还可以进行旋转，那些之前无法并排接入的插座终于可以同时使用了。除此之外，Stacked 还自带电压保护器和两个 USB 接口，能够满足大部分日常需求。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.stackedmodular.com/store/stacked-modular-power-strip.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 30 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706223724uiew0n9NfjS3xmrd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706223724VexGbWcm9HZiRotI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706223724dOCbwe9R8g2rztkT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070622373413i5RS6VaFbyp7ZO.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}